# Project Instructions (template)

## Project Description

A full-stack web application template built as a monorepo with a **Strapi** CMS backend and a **Next.js** frontend, orchestrated via **Docker Compose** with a **Caddy** reverse proxy handling SSL termination.

The project uses a multi-environment Docker Compose setup (`dev`, `prod`, `deploy`) managed through a single `manage.sh` CLI script. **Команды и сценарии использования manage.sh описаны в README.**

